findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to perform critical operations such as enabling trading, removing limits, disabling transfer delay, airdropping tokens, changing swapTokensAtAmount value, maximum transaction amount, fees, and more.

findings.title: Liquidity adding in wrong proportion
findings.description: Liquidity is added in an incorrect proportion.

findings.title: Liquidity pair contract’s security is not checked due to out of scope
findings.description: The audit did not check the security of the liquidity pair contract as it was deemed out of scope.
